{"tid":1785952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解未有人拎香港國旗出嚟","createTime":"2019-12-16T19:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T19:42:24.000Z","uid":231481,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4b0fab5d30fce3b447681cd95bf97f334a46bf","tid":1785952,"uid":231481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:13:27.000Z","msg":"依家大部份旗手都係拎光復旗同其他國家國家，但就好似未有人拎過香港國旗出嚟。其實早喺六月就已經有個國旗設計比賽，有啲熱心人設計咗一啲香港國旗出嚟，雖然個比賽係熱狗搞同埋得幾千人投票，但當中不乏好旗幟。我喺度放埋條link出嚟希望大家睇吓同討論吓國旗呢樣嘢。因為既然有國歌都好應該有國旗，相信如果有人整出嚟應該可以好似榮光咁振奮士氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/voteflag.php#94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fvoteflag.php%2394&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7kkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=22455edc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/voteflag.php#94</a>"},{"pid":"a477090252ebdde41c1febea16b1705db9017a61","tid":1785952,"uid":231481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:16:32.000Z","msg":"沉"},{"pid":"e4c782bf351348fa1eb47482a23ea64840e57993","tid":1785952,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:42:24.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差2萬人咋！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s